Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokaku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, why don't\Nyou leave this place, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and come live with your auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The city is a fun place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll have lots of friends at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got sweet candies\Nand interesting books...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do\Nthis training stuff anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister is sure to\Nhave wanted that for you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop spewing that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mother...\N--You are a disgrace to the Azumas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in no position to be speaking\Nwith the heir to the main family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are done visiting the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,be on your way back\Nto your mundane world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.10,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:34.82,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"SUB Fifth Riddle"\N"From kaiba@17_private_school.ac.jp"\N"How do you get a bird out of its cage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.82,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.83,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,There is no way out to run
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:53.88,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Don't get within lame firing range
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:58.89,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,It's a cold war zone,\Na boring state of affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:03.43,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ya know, it's because of us\Nthat things are unusual, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:08.23,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Long since overloaded and\Nthe self-ridicule is bottomless
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:12.90,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Hard to find the time to\Nshow any charming acts of folly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:17.53,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Only whipping things\Ninto a frenzy for nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:22.41,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Accept or rebel, only two choices?\NOh, the beauty of it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.04,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,"I won't let anyone touch her"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:29.29,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Traumatic innocence,\NI say that, but I'm one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:33.71,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,The reaping goes on\Nalways inexorably continuing on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.76,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,The truth of the hem of the skirt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:42.31,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Like an idiot,\Nyou just gotta believe in it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:47.23,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,That it got to you in a\Nway that was kind of scary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:52.98,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Just whisper it to\Nyourself plain and simple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.79,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Fifth Riddle"\N"How Do You Get a Bird Out of Its Cage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.71,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Year 10"\N"Class Black"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of this month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the Myojo Private School Anniversary\NFestival will finally be upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire school will be celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go all-out for this\Noccasion and put on a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class is full of beauties, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The play will be the classic of all\Nclassics--"Romeo and Juliet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.73,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Romeo and Juliet"\N"Year 10, Class Black"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teacher worked hard to\Nwrite up the script, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, turn to page ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that famous scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"O Romeo! wherefore art thou Romeo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.12,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"SUB Fifth Riddle"\N"From kaiba@17_private_school.ac.jp"\N"How do you get a bird out of its cage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--What a pain.\N--"If it is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count Isuke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you skip out,\Nyou won't get credit for the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.64,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Happy Anniversary"\N"Special Anniversary Festival Performance"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O Romeo, Romeo! wherefore art thou Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If it is thy wish, I am Romeo no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy lover, that will be my new name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How camest thou hither?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If they do see thee,\Nthey will murder thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There lies more peril in thine eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look thou but sweet, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing a male role is\Nall about the sex appeals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your sex appeal to make the\Nentire audience fall in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be more graceful!\NAnd passionate and sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Inviting sidelong looks!\NSlay the audience with your gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kenmochi, why don't you leave it at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mizorogi, please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shiena-{\i1}chan{\i0} is incredible.\N--Wrong! Wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--I hear she's into theatre and that sort of thing.\N--Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing isn't really me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so true. Juliet would've\Nsuited you better, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a lady,\Nafter all. Right, Miss Chitaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My vision won't be realized like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what they\Ncall a directorial vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Such enthusiasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.26,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Rear Garden Balcony (Night)"\N"N -> Right-handed? Callused palm (swordsmanship)"\N"K -> No physical strength (carries no weapons)"\N"N -> No acting ability" "K -> So-so actor"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Miss Haruki. That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no other redeeming\Nqualities, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Such work is beneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that goes over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll get it all done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the tests,\Nand now a school festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it?\NIt's very student-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But when all's said and done,\Neveryone seems to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We rarely get times like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haruki! It's all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Miss Haruki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Fuyuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ha-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Ha-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\N--No, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. Big Sis will\Ntake care of things for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? We're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace? School festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A bath. A bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A gigantic bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku, take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting out quickly\Nbefore anyone else comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will be coming anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially not at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Tokaku, Haru will wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I interrupt something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Nio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Having other people die for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that feel like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing someone and\Noutliving them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live with that and\Nstill keep a smile on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagae!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru {\i1}will{\i0} smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Azuma, she's saying\Nshe'll smile, even if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off. You're frightening Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're an Azuma?\NLook at how tame you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was done to you\Nthat you've been reduced to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you are now,\Neven I might be able to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ichinose, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh, Miss Tokaku?\N--Ichinose, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a little angry at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it burn you up?\NHaving those things said. To you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the point in\Nyou getting angry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haruki seemed different\Nthan usual, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could something have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Miss Tokaku's family that incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible doesn't even cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In these circles, the name Azuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a soul\Nwho hasn't heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A clan of assassins\Nthat's reigned supreme
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,over the dark side of this\Ncountry since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Azumas of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kuzunohas of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In every era, they've served those in power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,secretly altering the course of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Class Black, Rule 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-ho! Miss Tokaku,\Ncurry again? You sure must love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can know outside\Nof those in the class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the arbitrator, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got questions,\Ndon't ask that nobody. Ask me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, what about\Nlike your family structure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, a marital negotiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, I don't even know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother died immediately after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was raised by my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As for other relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually got no one in the world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.78,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Messages" "SUB Fifth Riddle"\N"From kaiba@17_private_school.ac.jp"\N"How do you get a bird out of its cage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,From your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some stuff on my mind\Nand I ended up lashing out at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, another peaceful day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If things were normal, Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0}\Nshould be there on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like any of us came\Nhere because we really wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bad luck do you suppose it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to\Ngive Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0} her freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From everything\Nthat's keeping her bound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For {\i1}us{\i0} to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Break away from the rules of Class Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,10 o'clock tonight. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk more then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Isuke's always lived her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only wasting time thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is short, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to quickly\Nget rid of what you don't need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and get free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was giving you advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.03,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Kuzunohas of the West, Azumas of the East"\N"- Assassin clans that have existed in\Nthis country since ancient times. -"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.74,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Originally, Kuzunoha was the\Nmain family and Azuma was the\Nbranch family. At present, exchanges between\Nthe two families have all but ceased."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reward I got for\Nthe first person I killed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,went to buying a tableful\Nof smiles for my family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the baby pink nail\Npolish that I'd always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew from\Nthe start that it wouldn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as your reward goes, Miss Haruki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been informed of it\Nsince you were invited to Class Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Money enough to\Nkeep your family well-fed for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing\NI want to make sure of, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.26,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Happy Anniversary"\N"Special Anniversary Festival Performance"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to see Haru about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haruki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, have you seen Miss Tokaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She left a note saying\Nthere was an urgent matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's Azuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,she's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.10,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"No. 06" "Haruki Sagae"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to blow\Noff our meeting from the get-go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I never lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to give Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0} her freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only way for\Nher to be free of all her shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss... To...ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be an Azuma,\Nbut the way you are now, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...can't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tokaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss To--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to\Nsacrifice to become that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Still want to keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no backing down from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for you guys and not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no escape,\Nno matter where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To become free,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing\NI want to make sure of, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the reward will\Nget to my family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all live on with\Nsmiles on your faces, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Haru-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.50,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Happy Anniversary"\N"Special Anniversary Festival Performance"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haruki's stage set...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It created a pocket of space for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No fatal wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, I lost. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was to make\Nit a clean death for all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't die. Not so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because being alive\Nmeans that you're being forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiven, to be here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I asked for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about unwanted meddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, looks like I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one way or another,\NI guess I'll have to keep at it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?\NYou look relieved that I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like this\Nmeans you can't die yet, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so you do your best to keep at it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Sis Haruki comes home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the best when\Nour family is all together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"SUB Re: Fifth Riddle"\N"To kaiba@17_private_school.ac.jp"\N"How, do you get a bird out of its cage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.66,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"SUB Re: Fifth Riddle"\N"To kaiba@17_private_school.ac.jp"\N">> How, do you get a bird out of its cage?"\N"Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.21,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,">> How do you get a bird out of its cage?"\N"Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:13.63,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,>> How do you get a bird out of its cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still say that\Nthe world is full of forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after what you've been put through...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the entire class and\Nthe entire world wanting you dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still forgive it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is about forgiving the mistakes\Nand crimes of those who are remorseful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It means forgiving\Nan infinite number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.43,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Just-for-show sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.39,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,You can lay it on all you want
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.27,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,The body is honest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:13.64,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Not enough, not satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:19.48,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,I want to keep the promise I made\Nher if it's the last thing I do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:24.20,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tying up my shoelaces nice and tight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:30.95,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,I can say I'd willingly give up even my life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.79,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Is there a wish that\Nyou've got there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:37.38,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Oh, set me free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.05,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Even pain and sacrifice are no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.30,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Set me free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.97,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,False kindness, that's over now too
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:51.31,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,To have hopes pinned on me,\Nto take on the burden
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:54.39,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Those things turn to strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.23,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,The meaning of living, the meaning of ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:01.78,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Because I know those\Nthings are here inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:05.95,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Please, set me free
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:21.55,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,No-big-deal sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To be or not to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To live or to die, that is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a line from "Hamlet."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The play in production is "Romeo and Juliet,"\Nso you say it's not relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:39.27,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Sixth Riddle"\N"Every Pretty Flower Has Its ___"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all giddy about the school\Nfestival and you're going to get hurt.
